targets.rawSql: SELECT MAX(betAmount) FROM roobet.bet WHERE IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game' AND $__timeFilter(createdAt);
SELECT AVG(betAmount) FROM roobet.bet WHERE IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game' AND $__timeFilter(createdAt);
SELECT AVG(profit) FROM roobet.bet WHERE IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game' AND $__timeFilter(createdAt);

SELECT 
  $__timeGroupAlias(createdAt,'$timerange'), 
  SUM(-profit) AS 'Casino Profit'
FROM bet
WHERE $__timeFilter(createdAt) AND IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(createdAt,'$timerange')

SELECT 
  $__timeGroupAlias(createdAt,'$timerange'), 
  SUM(betAmount) AS 'Total Bet Amount'
FROM bet
WHERE $__timeFilter(createdAt) AND IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(createdAt,'$timerange')

SELECT 
  $__timeGroupAlias(createdAt,'$timerange'), 
  COUNT(betId) AS 'Total Bets'
FROM bet
WHERE $__timeFilter(createdAt) AND IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(createdAt,'$timerange')

SELECT 
  $__timeGroupAlias(createdAt,'$timerange'), 
  COUNT(DISTINCT userId) AS 'Distinct Players'
FROM bet
WHERE IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
AND $__timeFilter(createdAt)
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(createdAt,'$timerange')

SELECT 
  $__timeGroupAlias(createdAt,'$timerange'), 
  MAX(profit) AS 'Max Win'
FROM bet
WHERE $__timeFilter(createdAt) AND IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(createdAt,'$timerange')

SELECT 
  $__timeGroupAlias(createdAt,'$timerange'),
  (COUNT(CASE WHEN profit > 0 THEN 1 END) / COUNT(*)) * 100 AS 'Profit Percentage'
FROM bet
WHERE $__timeFilter(createdAt) AND IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(createdAt,'$timerange')

SELECT 
  $__timeGroupAlias(createdAt,'$timerange'), 
  AVG(betAmount) AS 'Avg Bet Amount'
FROM bet
WHERE $__timeFilter(createdAt) AND IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(createdAt,'$timerange')

SELECT 
  $__timeGroupAlias(createdAt,'$timerange'), 
  MIN(profit) AS 'Min Profit'
FROM bet
WHERE $__timeFilter(createdAt) AND IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(createdAt,'$timerange')

SELECT IFNULL(u.name, 'anonymous') AS username, SUM(b.betAmount) AS totalBetAmount, SUM(b.profit) AS totalProfit
FROM bet b
LEFT JOIN users u ON b.userId = u.id
WHERE b.betAmount IS NOT NULL AND $__timeFilter(createdAt) AND IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
GROUP BY b.userId
ORDER BY totalBetAmount DESC
LIMIT 300;

panels.title: Users who wagered the most money

targets.rawSql:
SELECT IFNULL(u.name, 'anonymous') AS username, SUM(b.betAmount) AS totalBetAmount, SUM(b.profit) AS totalProfit
FROM bet b
LEFT JOIN users u ON b.userId = u.id
WHERE b.profit IS NOT NULL AND $__timeFilter(createdAt) AND IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
GROUP BY b.userId
ORDER BY totalProfit DESC
LIMIT 300;

panels.title: Users with the highest total profit

targets.rawSql:
SELECT IFNULL(u.name, 'anonymous') AS username, SUM(b.betAmount) AS totalBetAmount, SUM(b.profit) AS totalProfit
FROM bet b
LEFT JOIN users u ON b.userId = u.id
WHERE b.profit IS NOT NULL AND $__timeFilter(createdAt) AND IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
GROUP BY b.userId
ORDER BY totalProfit ASC
LIMIT 300;

panels.title: Users with the lowest total profit

targets.rawSql:
SELECT IFNULL(u.name, 'anonymous') AS username, COUNT(*) AS numBets, SUM(b.betAmount) AS totalBetAmount, SUM(b.profit) AS totalProfit, MAX(b.profit) AS maxWin, MIN(b.profit) AS maxLose, AVG(b.profit) AS avgProfit, MAX(b.betAmount) AS maxBetAmount, MIN(b.betAmount) AS minBetAmount, AVG(b.betAmount) AS avgBetAmount
FROM bet b
LEFT JOIN users u ON b.userId = u.id
WHERE $__timeFilter(b.createdAt) AND IFNULL(gameNameDisplay, gameName) = '$game'
GROUP BY b.userId
ORDER BY numBets DESC
LIMIT 300;
